    "description": "Droom Ventures Solutions, one of India's leading organizations, is hiring a Category Manager for our Jabalpur operations. We offer a competitive salary package along with world-class benefits.\n\nAbout Droom Ventures Solutions:\nDroom Ventures Solutions is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Build and maintain affiliate and influencer marketing programs\n• Manage marketplace relationships with Amazon, Flipkart, and Meesho\n• Conduct competitor analysis and market benchmarking\n• Execute digital marketing campaigns across Google, Meta, and other channels\n• Collaborate with logistics partners to ensure timely delivery\n• Analyze sales data and customer behavior to drive revenue growth\n• Manage customer reviews, ratings, and return/refund processes\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBA from a recognized university\n• 1-3 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain\n• Proficiency in A/B Testing\n• Proficiency in Magento\n• Proficiency in SEO/SEM\n• Proficiency in Google Analytics\n• Proficiency in Performance Marketing\n• Proficiency in Influencer Marketing\n• Proficiency in Digital Marketing\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Learning & development budget\n• Referral bonus program\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Flexible working hours\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Salary Range: 4 LPA - 9 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Jabalpur, Madhya Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Droom Ventures Solutions!",
